'''Devuan''' ,是Debian GNU/Linux发行版的一个衍生版。<ref name=PCWorld>{{cite web|last1=Hoffman|first1=Chris|title=Meet Devuan, the Debian fork born from a bitter systemd revolt|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2854717/meet-devuan-the-debian-fork-born-from-a-bitter-systemd-revolt.html|website=PCWorld|accessdate=13 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209075125/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2854717/meet-devuan-the-debian-fork-born-from-a-bitter-systemd-revolt.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Phoronix>{{cite web|last1=Larabel|first1=Michael|title=Devuan: Debian Without Systemd|url=http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTg1MDQ|website=Phoronix|accessdate=14 December 2014|archive-date=2015-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317190237/http://www.phoronix.com/scan.php?page=news_item&px=MTg1MDQ|dead-url=yes}}</ref>该发行版的发行目的是创建一个没有争议性软件[[systemd|systemd]]的发行版。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sharwood|first1=Simon|title=systemd row ends with Debian getting forked|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/12/01/ttsystemdtt_row_ends_with_debian_getting_forked/|website=The Register|accessdate=13 December 2014|archivedate=2014-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213034735/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/12/01/ttsystemdtt_row_ends_with_debian_getting_forked/|dead-url=no}}</ref> Debian 8 "Jessie"由于将systemd作为默认的初始化程序([[init|init]])，在开发者及用户中产生了诸多的争议。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://news.softpedia.com/news/Fork-Debian-Project-Announces-the-Systemd-less-OS-Devuan-466178.shtml | title=Fork Debian Project Announces the Systemd-less OS Devuan | work=Softpedia | date=28 November 2014 | accessdate=30 November 2014 | author=Stahie, Silviu | archive-date=2014-11-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141130142144/http://news.softpedia.com/news/Fork-Debian-Project-Announces-the-Systemd-less-OS-Devuan-466178.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://lists.dyne.org/lurker/message/20141130.155131.7e186914.en.html | title=Re: [Dng] I want systemd | work=Dng -- The first mailinglist after debianfork.org | date=30 November 2014 | accessdate=4 December 2014 | author=Lanza, Franco | archive-date=2014-12-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209235450/https://lists.dyne.org/lurker/message/20141130.155131.7e186914.en.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://lists.debian.org/debian-announce/2015/msg00001.html | title=Debian 8 "Jessie" released | work=debian-announce | date=2015-04-25 | accessdate=2015-04-26 | author=Wise, Paul | archive-date=2015-05-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518080452/https://lists.debian.org/debian-announce/2015/msg00001.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

